		This article was co-authored by <a href="/Author/Tu-Anh-Vu-DMD">Tu Anh Vu, DMD</a> and by wikiHow staff writer, <a href="/Author/Dan-Hickey">Dan Hickey</a>. Dr. Tu Anh Vu is a Board Certified Dentist and Owner of Tu's Dental, her private practice, in Brooklyn, New York. With over six years of clinical experience, Dr. Vu helps adults and kids of all ages get over their anxiety with dental phobia. Dr. Vu has conducted research related to finding the cure for Kaposi Sarcoma cancer and has presented her research at the Hinman Meeting in Memphis. She received her undergraduate degree from Bryn Mawr College and a DMD from the University of Pennsylvania School of Dental Medicine.

