<div class="mf-section-0" id="mf-section-0"><p>“Tongue posture” sounds like a bizarre concept (doesn’t it just lie there?), but the position of your tongue at rest can have implications for your overall health and well-being. In this article, we’ll show you what correct tongue posture looks like, plus how to tell if your tongue position is off and what to do to correct the problem. Read on to learn more (and see if you can keep your tongue in the right shape while you scroll!).
</p></div>
