<script>WH.ads.addBodyAd('scrollto_ad_1')</script><div class="section whatistongueposture before_steps_section sticky font_test">
<div class="headline_container "><div class="headline_info">
<span id="What-is-tongue-posture?"></span><h2 class="section-heading" onclick="javascript:mfTempOpenSection(1)">
<div class="mw-ui-icon mw-ui-icon-element indicator"></div>
<span class="mw-headline" id="What-is-tongue-posture.3F">What is tongue posture?</span>
</h2>
</div></div>
<div id="whatistongueposture" class="section_text">
<p>Tongue posture is the position of your tongue at rest. Ideally, the tip of the tongue sits on the roof of the mouth behind the teeth while the rest of the tongue runs along the hard palate with lips closed and both rows of teeth lightly touching. Poor posture can lead to misaligned teeth, a narrow jaw, or sleep apnea.
</p>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="wh_ad_inner w_label al_grey gam" data-service="dfp" data-instantload="1" data-adunitpath="/10095428/engl/engl_gam_all_scrol" data-size="[728, 90]" data-prebidload="1" data-apsload="1" data-aps-timeout="800" data-width="728" data-height="90" data-innerclass="gam" data-type="prestep" data-large="1" data-medium="1" data-channels="4657739586" data-aditudetarget="pb-slot-engl-scrol" data-largechannels="2060152247,5763098696" data-smallchannels="8156154280" data-mediumchannels="4066873649" data-pagetype="methods" data-observerloading="1" data-sizes-array="[728, 90]" data-gptdisplaylate="1" data-pbadunits='{"appnexus":19512208,"pubmatic":"2946818","ix":"531046","amx":"d2lraWhvdy5jb20","rubicon":"1753134","shemedia":"2952570","openx":"541138162","triplelift":"Wikihow_engl_gam_all_728x90_Prebid","yahooAds":"8a96954f01747430358b365459b80331","yieldmo":"2508866731741487190","grid":168908,"medianet":"464704332","rise":"engl_gam_all_scrol","sharethrough":"YRwAUQ4n3r0xdDMH0TOrPfnH"}'><div id="prestep_ad_1" class="gam blockthrough"></div></div>
